race-gate
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:the swing-gate or drafting gate in a race, through which sheep pass in single-file.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
